img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事實：<br />\n無用個app先會比人盜用<br />\n應該快啲登記哂全部支那app，bind哂全部信用卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n理想：<br />\n取締支那app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"取乜鳩野締<br />\n市面大把替代品<br />\n又Apple 又Google pay<br />\n做乜撚要用支那app?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:41:28.000Z","msg":"唔取締咪有個窿比人盜用囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78ff4dbb993fb58593701c8e7350af62cce6ff5","tid":886181,"uid":470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:42:25.000Z","msg":"成班child登仔都唔知問題喺邊<br />\n唔識對症下藥<br />\n淨係反反反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2f08beaf630140f78d15c769d783dc68da595f","tid":886181,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以呢個年代，迫香港銀行可以將信用咭交易Real-time check到仲實際，喺歐洲好多Debit Card都做到嘅事，香港啲Credit Card話做唔到，真係有無搞錯。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n安信張垃圾卡個App都做到嘅嘢，反而好多大行做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbc40d81368633e6bba2b11676b00af9cade9d5","tid":886181,"uid":180373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:44:16.000Z","msg":"tap &amp; go咪又係一樣漏洞多"}]}